verbose_text: In our study, incorporation of pIL-15 by DMA resulted in higher intracellular uptake of IL-15 DNA, causing higher levels of transcription and higher levels of secreted IL-15, and improving the anti-tumor efficiency of cytokine gene transfer.
evidence: pIL-15 by DMA resulted in higher intracellular uptake of IL-15 DNA, causing higher levels of transcription
